To use this script, you'll need a few non-standard python libraries:
IMDbPY: http://imdbpy.sourceforge.net/
Installation: sudo apt-get install python-imdbpy

themoviedb: http://github.com/dbr/themoviedb
Installation: a copy of the module is included pyXBMCscrape, just unzip it to the same folder as the script

lxml: http://codespeak.net/lxml/
Installation: sudo apt-get install python-lxml

Help:
Basic Usage: pyXBMCscrape.py filename

To print a list of command line parameters: pyXBMCscrape.py -h
